  not permitted.

The error appears in the following stanza:

  irrelevant-files: &tempest-irrelevant-files
                - ^(test-|)requirements.txt$
                - ^.*\.rst$
                - ^api-ref/.*$
                - ^glance/hacking/.*$
                - ^glance/locale/.*$
                - ^glance/tests/.*$
                - ^doc/.*$
                - ^releasenotes/.*$
                - ^tools/.*$
                - ^tox.ini$
